{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260419190800","title":"Judgement senior harus di-infrastrukturkan sebagai executable instruction AI","desc":"Insight dari artikel yang menekankan bahwa prompt AI tim adalah artefak engineering, bukan hanya teks sekali pakai.","tags":["permanent-note","ai","governance","prompt-engineering"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"da6c65071b6ffa0689a457a0e6d2284c","updated":1776914280016,"created":1776914280016,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","id":"zettel.20260419190800","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","id":"zettel.20260419190800","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.ai","alias":"ai","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.ai"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","id":"zettel.20260419190800","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.governance","alias":"governance","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.governance"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","id":"zettel.20260419190800","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.prompt-engineering","alias":"prompt-engineering","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.prompt-engineering"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419190800","id":"zettel.20260419190800","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":18,"offset":729},"end":{"line":19,"column":63,"offset":774},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":100,"column":3,"offset":8609},"end":{"line":100,"column":28,"offset":8634},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419190800"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260419192239","id":"zettel.20260419192239","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":21,"column":3,"offset":849},"end":{"line":21,"column":28,"offset":874},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419190800"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","id":"zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":96,"column":3,"offset":4139},"end":{"line":96,"column":28,"offset":4164},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260419190800"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"judgement-senior-harus-di-infrastrukturkan-sebagai-executable-instruction-ai\">Judgement senior harus di-infrastrukturkan sebagai executable instruction AI<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#judgement-senior-harus-di-infrastrukturkan-sebagai-executable-instruction-ai\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Instruksi AI tim bukan cuma teks; ia adalah infrastruktur yang menyimpan dan menyalurkan judgment senior secara konsisten.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ketika satu senior mencoba menerapkan standar lewat prompt, hasilnya tergantung pada siapa yang menulis.</li>\n<li>Jika judgement itu tetap tacit dan personal, AI tidak akan membuat kualitas tim menjadi konsisten.</li>\n<li>Oleh karena itu instruksi tim harus:\n<ul>\n<li>ditulis secara eksplisit,</li>\n<li>disimpan di repo,</li>\n<li>direview bersama,</li>\n<li>dijalankan oleh workflow AI.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Ini mengubah prompt engineering dari productivity hack pribadi menjadi governance teknis.</li>\n<li>Ini juga berarti tim harus membangun feedback loop terhadap instruksi itu, sama seperti kode, lint, atau CI.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>→ Dikuatkan oleh <a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards\">Encoding Team Standards — executable AI instruction untuk konsistensi tim</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">governance (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">prompt-engineering (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260419192239\">Executable governance adalah standar tim yang bukan hanya ditulis, tapi dijalankan oleh AI</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.encoding-team-standards\">Encoding Team Standards — executable AI instruction untuk konsistensi tim</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":t